
-------------------  A current list of emotes  ---------------------

ilook     Show everyone how innocent you are.
laff      Laff like a Lunar.
didit     Show everyone how you MEANT to do that.
wuss      Call people a "wuss".
muah      Show everyone how powerful you are with a "MUAH"!
shoo      People would like it if you are about to fail a spell and know it.
wise      Tell someone "wise".
nog2      Nognog for that extra bit of pazazz.
lmdoit    Tell 'em how the Lunars do "it".
thump     Give them a thump to the head.
lmdrop    Drop to all fours and ask the moons for luck.
ffeud     For a high five and a "good answer".
wisdom    Proclaim "wisdom".
mburn     Shoot a seering ray of light at whomever you want.
redimp    Make the red moon glow violently.
megimp    Make the magenta moon fade in and out.
greimp    Make the green moon move in the sky.
chant     Tell everyone what the best guild is.

lmpose    A multisection emote that gets better at differant levels.

